@node WSTEP "Introduction"
 Hingis'99 is a database about singles matches of @{"Martina Hingis" link Hingis} in season 1999.
It contains data about matches, statistics, bios and @{FG shine}WTA Tour@{FG text} ranking.

@endnode

@node INSTALACJA "Instalation"
 
The program may be installed using standard installer, but it will also run from any place
on your disk. Then you only need to install fonts in FONTS:. If you don't know how
to do it, read your System Manual.
You should also adjust @{"screen colors" link KOLORY} in Turbo Calc.

@endnode

